data.description: Welcome to a quaint and quiet family home situated on a 2.03 acre lot in the well-known community of Blue Heron Estates.  With a large driveway and abundance of parking, this home sits approximately 200 ft from the roadway.   The lot has plenty of large mature trees and trees encompass the rear property lines, giving this home a lot of grass area, all while in a community.    This home features a bedroom and full bath on the first floor, in addition to an eat-in kitchen, family area,  and a large sunroom on the rear of the property.  In the sunroom is a cozy wood fireplace for all these chilly winter evenings.  The home has hardwood and upgraded LVP flooring on this first floor common area.  The kitchen features gorgeous stainless steel appliances while maintaining the woodsy charm of the surrounding area.  The second floor has the master bedroom with attached full bathroom and two additional bedrooms and another full bath.  The fourth bedroom could easily be a large playroom or game room, the possibilities are endless with that space.  There is plenty of storage in this property between the oversized two car garage and the 3rd floor storage area accessible through one of the 2nd floor bedrooms.    Some furniture in the property is negotiable for sale, not included in the price.  The water pump was upgraded to a 1/2 HP Pump the end of January 2024.   This home is move in ready! Come take a tour today!
